cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper discusses the use of crowdsourcing and machine learning for natural language processing tasks, specifically medical relation extraction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of cognitive computing systems, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of machine learning is also mentioned, which falls under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper discusses the use of crowdsourcing, which falls under the category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
